        {
            "text": "3. Shake for 30 min at room temperature to lyse the cells. This can be done using an orbital rotator or a shaker. (see Note 5) 4. Centrifuge the lysate at 22,000g for 30 min at 4\u00b0C, and transfer the supernatant to a clean 50 mL Falcon tube. Discard the pellet.",
